# Sonari — Agent Constitution

India-first jewellery billing + ERP SaaS. Plans live in `Plans/`. Full constitution: `Plans/18-ai-agent-manual.md`.

## Prime directives

1. **READ before WRITE** — read governing plans before any code
2. **REUSE before REBUILD** — search `packages/ui`, `packages/domain`, `packages/types` first
3. **ASK before ASSUME** — never invent business rules; ask or ADR in `Plans/DECISIONS.md`
4. **Never ship N+1** — batch, join, or embed; never query-in-loop
5. **UPDATE plans in the same change** when reality changes — **proactively, never wait to be asked** (see `sonari-plans-sync` rule)

## Pre-task ritual (output before coding)

```
Task: <one-line>
Read: ✓ 00-MASTER-PLAN ✓ 15-coding-standards ✓ 18-ai-agent-manual ✓ <task plans>
Modules impacted: <apps/packages/tables>
Contracts: <API, Zod, RLS>
Questions: <or None>
```

If any question is non-trivial → **stop and ask** (options + recommendation).

